//Fibonacci sequence
// 0 1 1 2 3 5 8 13 21

// takes n as a parameter and gives you the n'th fib
// Repeated action: add the last number to the last last number
// Stop Condition: when we hit the nth number.

fib n
| n == 1 = 0
| n == 2 = 1
= fib (n-1) + fib (n-2)
